{"abstract": "Robert Dudley, an American, will take over leadership of the company after repeated stumbles by Tony Hayward in responding to the oil spill in the Gulf of Mexico.", "web_url": "https://www.nytimes.com/2010/07/26/business/global/26bp.html", "snippet": "Robert Dudley, an American, will take over leadership of the company after repeated stumbles by Tony Hayward in responding to the oil spill in the Gulf of Mexico.", "lead_paragraph": "BP\u2019s board is expected on Monday to name an American, Robert Dudley, as its chief executive, replacing Tony Hayward, whose repeated stumbles during the company\u2019s three-month oil spill in the Gulf of Mexico alienated federal and state officials as well as residents of the Gulf Coast. ", "print_section": "A", "print_page": "1", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2010/07/25/business/bp/bp-jumbo.jpg", "height": 665, "width": 1024, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "thumbnail", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2010/07/25/business/bp/bp-thumbStandard.jpg", "height": 75, "width": 75, "subType": "thumbnail", "crop_name": "thumbStandard", "legacy": {"thumbnail": "images/2010/07/25/business/bp/bp-thumbStandard.jpg", "thumbnailwidth": 75, "thumbnailheight": 75}}], "headline": {"main": "BP Is Expected to Replace Chief With American", "kicker": null, "content_kicker": null, "print_headline": "BP Is Expected To Replace Chief With American", "name": null, "seo": null, "sub": null}, "keywords": [{"name": "organizations", "value": "BP Plc", "rank": 1, "major": "N"}, {"name": "glocations", "value": "Gulf of Mexico", "rank": 2, "major": "N"}, {"name": "persons", "value": "Hayward, Tony", "rank": 3, "major": "N"}, {"name": "subject", "value": "Appointments and Executive Changes", "rank": 4, "major": "N"}, {"name": "subject", "value": "Accidents and Sa